        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Gigantochloa glabrata N. H. Xia & Y. Zeng ex D. Z. Li & Z. C. Xu A-C culm D, F culm sheath E, I leaf G flower branches H, J pseudospikelet K, L glume M lemma (l), palea (p), ovary (o), stamens (st). Scale bars: 1 m (A); 3 cm (C); 1 cm (E, H)." , "Figure 1. Gigantochloa glabrata N. H. Xia & Y. Zeng ex D. Z. Li & Z. C. Xu A leaf branch B flowering branch C culm sheath D leaf ligule E pseudospikelet F inflorescence G lemma H anthers I pistil J palea. Drawn from the type specimen and pictures by Yi-Fan Li. Scale bars: 2 cm (A-C); 8 mm (G-J); 4 mm (D-F)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489418" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/489417" .

